title: Conker Live & Reloaded (for xbox 360)
description:
This is a complete rip of Conker Live & Reloaded (2005), an original xbox game.

To burn this image, you must use dual layer DVD. Imgburn is recommended.

This is the NTSC version of the game, it works on a flashed NTSC Xbox 360 console.

You will need a file archiver like 7-Zip, to open the file.

Note: This won't work on an Xbox console, unless unpacked, and repacked
